00:41:37.873 --> 00:41:43.550
phenomena on macroscopic
particles has not been observed,

00:41:43.550 --> 00:41:47.706
because our wavelengths,
your wavelengths,

00:41:47.706 --> 00:41:51.356
my wavelengths,
baseball wavelengths,

00:41:51.356 --> 00:41:54.904
these wavelengths are way too
small.

00:41:54.904 --> 00:42:02.000
They're way too small because
