00:43:35.282 --> 00:43:38.929
phenomena.
You see those effects of those

00:43:38.929 --> 00:43:43.670
wave-like properties.
And it is just that realization

00:43:43.670 --> 00:43:48.047
that led Schrödinger here,
who is now washed out,

00:43:48.047 --> 00:43:51.785
to write down the wave equation
of motion.

00:43:51.785 --> 00:43:56.435
And that's an equation of
motion for particles whose

00:43:56.435 --> 00:44:03.000
wavelength is on the order of
the size of their environment.

00:44:03.000 --> 00:44:08.086
And you have to use that
equation of motion to understand

00:44:08.086 --> 00:44:10.810
how that electron,
